                        "displayName": "Will Jones",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
                    },
                    "body": "PyArrow and adlfs work because we implement a compatibility layer between Python fsspec filesystems and PyArrow filesystems.\r\n\r\nIIUC you are suggesting we could implement some similar integration in R? Does there exist a standard protocol analogous to fsspec?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=willjones127",
                        "name": "willjones127",
                        "key": "willjones127",
                        "avatarUrls": {
